sentences.english: Contact shipping companies, and complete declaration of export commodities and inspection work.
sentences.chinese: 聯繫船運公司，並完成出口商品的報關和報檢工作。

sentences.english: And China is the biggest merchandise exporter to the Middle East.
sentences.chinese: 而中國是最大的往中東出口商品的國家。

sentences.english: Export commodities may not by exported without an inspection.
sentences.chinese: 出口商品未經檢驗的，不準出口。

sentences.english: In compliance dawn ywe request, we are not sending you, under separate cover, we latest catalogue or price list covering we export range.
sentences.chinese: 謹遵要求另函奉上最新之出口商品列表和報價單。

sentences.english: We hope to horle as an agent the bads you are not exporting.
sentences.chinese: 咱們願意擔任你們出口商品的代理。

sentences.english: The dollar’s recent revival will make America’s exports dearer.
sentences.chinese: 最近美元的重新升值使得美國出口商品更貴。

sentences.english: A: Our exports have to pass a rigid inspection before they are shipped.
sentences.chinese: 我們的出口商品必須在裝運前經過一道嚴格的檢查。

sentences.english: We generally insure our export shipment with the People'sInsurance Company of China.
sentences.chinese: 通常我們向中國人民保險公司爲我們的出口商品投保。

sentences.english: This paper is used only for applying for inspection or certificate-change of directly exported commodities.
sentences.chinese: 此單僅用於直髮出口商品的檢驗或換證申報。

sentences.english: Tianjin Small Red Beans have a long export history. They are our traditional export product.
sentences.chinese: 天津紅小豆出口歷史悠久，是天津傳統出口商品。

sentences.english: The total shipment will be invoiced to you at 10% below export list prices.
sentences.chinese: 全部貨物將按低於出口商品價格的10%開發票給你。

sentences.english: Thailand is by far the largest buyer of Burmese exports.
sentences.chinese: 迄今，泰國是緬甸出口商品的最大購買方。

sentences.english: On display are more than40,000 samples of export commodities.
sentences.chinese: 陳列的出口商品的樣品共四萬多種。

sentences.english: I acted as an interpreter for three times at Guangzhou Export Commodities Fair.
sentences.chinese: 我曾三次爲廣州出口商品交易會做譯員。

sentences.english: Its number-one export to China was, apparently, tobacco.
sentences.chinese: 菸草是它對中國的第一大出口商品。

sentences.english: The irrevocable L/C gives your exports the protection of a banker's guarantee.
sentences.chinese: 不可撤銷的信用證會使你方出口商品得到銀行的擔保。
